        "description": "Match records from the 2022-2025 season, including matches that have not occurred yet. I included a link for each match to find additional information on it. The dataset is meant to be used in educational purposes, for programmers to create and test predictive algorithms. It's still a work in progress... \n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThis is a dataset containing records of all premier league matches since 2022/2023 season, plus uncompleted matches for the 2024/2025 season.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nMatchday: Game's matchday for that season\nDate: Date of match\nTime: Time match started in UK time\nHome Team: Home team for that game\nhomeScore: Amount of goals scored by home team\nhomeXG: Expected goals for home team\nawayScore: Amount of goals scored by away team\nawayXG: Expected goals for away team\nAway Team: Away team for that match\nAttendance: Amount of people attending stadium of match\nReferee: [no description]\nStadium: [no description]\nResult: [no description]\n*Additional Stats: [no description]\n",
